greetings my name is Matt word and I'm
here at the AWS headquarters in Seattle
to announce the general availability of
Amazon Kinesis analytics Kinesis
analytics brings real-time stream
processing to all developers all you
need to know is standard SQL Kinesis
analytics does all the heavy lifting to
run your SQL queries continuously on
realtime streaming data while it is
still in transit you don't even have to
wait for it to get written to a database
Kinesis analytics allows you to Launch
stre processing in just a few minutes
Kinesis analytics recognizes standard
data formats such as Json CSV and tsv
and includes automatic schema building
and editing tools then it lets you write
SQL against that data as if it was in a
table that was being updated continually
we also give you pre-built templates
that provide SQL code for common tasks
such as stream filtering anomaly
detection and topk Analysis and you can
use kesis analytics to deliver realtime
stream processing with sub 1second
latencies for use cases such as I T
clickstream analysis adtech gaming and
more Kinesis analytics is available to
all customers from today thanks a lot
